With respect to my original answer (the bit above the first horizontal line), it was deliberately glib because in *most cases*, [this type of micro-optimising is not good][2].


  [1]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7115445/what-is-the-optimal-capacity-and-load-factor-for-a-fixed-size-hashmap/7115550#7115550
